short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Navigate to any subreddit quickly from the search bar

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
To use this extension type "r/ " into the navigation bar, and then type the name of the subreddit you want to navigate to.

You can choose whether or not to go to www.reddit.com or old.reddit.com.
